      <title>迪拜交易所准备在二次发行中出售股票，纳斯达克股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/nasdaq-stock-falls-borse-dubai-set-sell-shares-secondary-offering-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，在迪拜交易所宣布进行二次发行股票以削减其在美国证券交易所的少数股权后，纳斯达克股票在周二的盘后交易中下跌超过 2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/nasdaq-stock-falls-borse-dubai-set-sell-shares-secondary-offering-2024-03-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 01:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
