      <title>制药商远藤公司破产重组获得美国法院批准</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drugmaker-endo-receives-us-court-approval-bankruptcy-restructuring-2024-03-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[破产制药商远藤国际 (Endo International) 周二表示，美国破产法院已批准其重组计划和相关阿片类药物和解方案，以摆脱 2022 年开始的破产保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drugmaker-endo-receives-us-court-approval-bankruptcy-restructuring-2024-03-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 22:42:45 GMT</pubDate>
